<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>اسْمُهُ لَيثٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٨٩١]</span> أَبُو رَزينَ العُقَيْليُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>اسْمُهُ لَقيطُ بنُ عامِرٍ.<span class="c5"> ويُقالُ:</span> ابنُ صَبِرةَ بنِ المُنْتفِقِ، لهُ صُحبةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٨٩٢]</span> أَبُو العَلانِيةِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>اسْمُهُ مُسْلِمٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٨٩٣]</span> أَبُو حَسّانَ الأَعْرجُ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>اسْمُهُ مُسْلِمٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٨٩٤]</span> أَبُو نُصَيرةَ الوَاسِطِيُّ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>اسْمُهُ مُسْلمُ بنُ عُبَيدٍ الوَاسِطيُّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٨٩٥]</span> أَبُو دَاودَ الأَحْمَرِيُّ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>اسمُهُ مَالكٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٨٩٦]</span> أَبُو الرِّجالِ <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>اسْمُهُ مُحمدُ بنُ عبدِ الرَّحمنِ الأَنْصاريُّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
